  "details": "The container-tools module contains tools for working with containers, notably podman, buildah, skopeo, and runc.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * net/[http:](http:) Request smuggling due to acceptance of invalid chunked data in net/http (CVE-2025-22871)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
